datosLaboralesPOJO.descripcion: Discovery of novel tropical plants with anticancer activities. Duties and activities: Organize the cell culture room and experimental approaches to test tropical fruit extracts on cancer cells. Selected extracts with strong effect on cell survival and/or migration were further studied to understand their mechanism of action. Here I was in charge of a) Teaching students and other scientist to perform experiments with breast cancer cells, b) designing and performing experiments.

Design, perform and interpretation of in vitro and in vivo experiments to target proliferation and migration of breast cancer cells using novel nanoparticles based on high-density lipoproteins (sHDL). Here, I was in charge of: a) producing/purifying recombinant apolipoprotein A1 in bacteria for synthesis of lipoprotein nanoparticles, b) testing anti-proliferative and anti-migratory effects in breast cancer cell lines, c) injection of cancer cells in nude mice.

Design and perform in vitro experiments to identify master regulator genes expressed in gastric cancer stem cell and identify new CpG-methylated genes in gastric cancer. Here, I was in charge of: a) setting up the laboratory since my supervisor moved from another university, b) production of lentiviral particles, c) culture of gastric cancer cells and gastric cancer stem cells, d) mRNA in situ detection in gastric tumor samples.

Design and perform experiments using in vitro and in vivo mouse models. Also, perform experiments to understand the role of SR-BI in breast cancer. Here, I was in charge of: a) cell culture of endothelial cells, macrophages
and vascular smooth muscle cells, b) deciphering cell signaling regulated by
caveolins, c) genotyping of double knock-out mice, d) tissue and blood
collection of mice prone to develop atherosclerosis, e) immunohistochemistry and immunofluorescence, f) presenting and writing r
Realización de experimentos relacionados al transporte ovular, análisis y presentación de resultados.
Ejecución de ensayos de evaluación de fertilidad masculina y de embarazo.
Participación en el proyecto El Fenómeno El Niño 1997-1998, realizando recolección de muestras y procesamiento histológico.
